275
00:21:20,763 --> 00:21:24,444
I see, well, guess there's nothing you can do about it.

276
00:21:25,652 --> 00:21:27,765
Yeah, right.

277
00:21:28,452 --> 00:21:29,273
I guess not.

278
00:21:36,584 --> 00:21:39,024
It really is a nice moon tonight.

279
00:21:40,863 --> 00:21:43,098
Fine, since you can't do it,

280
00:21:44,546 --> 00:21:46,331
I'm gonna be a hero for you.

281
00:21:47,339 --> 00:21:47,714
Hm?

282
00:21:48,001 --> 00:21:51,840
