285
00:22:07,652 --> 00:22:08,386
All right.

286
00:22:14,542 --> 00:22:15,444
You do that.

287
00:22:17,582 --> 00:22:18,934
I can rest easy now.

288
00:22:23,639 --> 00:22:26,746
Tell me, Kerry, what do you wanna grow up to be?

289
00:22:28,965 --> 00:22:29,706
Well...

